There will be many updates, some of which are serious.<br />
<br />
First of all, fusion will be removed due to the amount of abuse.<br />
<br />
Allied Fleets will be limited for the same reason.<br />
<br />
All bugs that caused the server to crash have been fixed.<br />
<br />
I have also selected an official Archspace Dev Team.<br />
<br />
I (Mindwarper) am the only system administrator and game administrator. No changes will be done unless I allow them, and if you want to report a critical bug you will have to use http://www.mlsecurity.com/contact.php (I will add links to this page).<br />
<br />
zbyte, DarkTempes, embryodead, and Taog are the programmers.<br />
<br />
<br />
Due to the large amount of multi's and the slow voting process in the anti-multi system, I have selected 4 super mods. These mods (currently unamed) have access to ban any player. If that player tries to login or continue playing he/she will get a message that they have banned and the reason.They will have send a message through contact.php or contact me or the super mods. If they do not contact us or their reason is not good enough, after 1 week the character will be removed completely, and if the player had multiple accounts, all of them will be removed.<br />
<br />
DarkTempes has posted a changelist in the player board. This list contains most of the small changes.<br />
<br />
Most of the crash bugs have been fixed. The next time (if there is one), whoever is responsible for a crash on purpose will be automatically removed, and anyone who knew about him/her and did not report earlier will be removed as well.<br />
<br />
Thanks,<br />
